title: GoPro: RC Tribute to Ken Block’s Gymkhana
description:
The guys at HPI Racing put their own spin on Ken Block's Gymkhana 6 using a RC car and a 1/18th scaled track.

Shot 100% on the HERO3+® camera 

Music
Viramaina "Bellz"
